				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8e28f17 elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode" data-id="8e28f17" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="shortcode.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-shortcode">        <div class="rplg" style="" data-id="1846"><div class="rplg-badge-cnt                     rplg-badge_left-fixed                                         rplg-badge-hide        "><div class="rplg-badge2"                                data-provider="google"            ><div class="rplg-badge2-border"></div><div class="rplg-badge2-btn rplg-badge2-clickable"                                    ><span class="rplg-badge-logo"></span><div class="rplg-badge2-score"><div>Google Bewertung</div><div ><div class="rplg-biz-rating rplg-trim rplg-biz-google"><div class="rplg-biz-score" >4.8</div><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="4.8,google,#0caa41"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form rplg-form-left" style="display:none"><div class="rplg-form-head"><div class="rplg-form-head-inner"><div class="rplg-row"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/places/ANXAkqFJGo_8G82rL4MbC4mSvmYVwavZ_qxD8SXgTo5W8mSzi1tplSqigyTzznblcDaWgbtavZ8yCMqSEX2blt50u29GtSfhL-vE-rw=s1600-w300-h300" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="rotknopf | Herrenschneider in Wien" width="50" height="50" title="rotknopf | Herrenschneider in Wien" onerror="if(this.src!='data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7')this.src='data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right rplg-trim">                                    rotknopf | Herrenschneider in Wien        <div ><div class="rplg-biz-rating rplg-trim rplg-biz-google"><div class="rplg-biz-score" >4.8</div><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="4.8,google,#0caa41"></div></div></div></div></div></div><button class="rplg-form-close" type="button" onclick="_rplg_get_parent(this, 'rplg-form').style.display='none'">×</button></div><div class="rplg-form-body"></div><div class="rplg-form-content"><div class="rplg-form-content-inner"><div class="rplg-form-review "><div class="rplg-row rplg-row-start"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLE1VMZDLI4uVQmZYo4px4dxjOsUB3R-c0K0OywldnDkaIsKw=s56-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="Carlos S." width="50" height="50" title="Carlos S." onerror="if(this.src!='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png')this.src='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right"><div class="rplg-review-name rplg-trim" title="Carlos S.">Carlos S.</div><div class="rplg-review-time rplg-trim" data-time="1761421922">19:52 25 Oct 25</div><div class="rplg-box-content"><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="5,google,#777"></div><span class="rplg-review-text">Can only recommend Rotknopf to anybody who is interested in getting a new suit or tux for a special occasion! I went there looking for a special tuxedo for my wedding and Oliver took me step by step into choosing the perfect one for the big day! The attention to detail was impeccable and the suggestions were great! Would definitely go again and would definitely recommend it to anybody who’s on the search for a special outfit! &#x1f44f;&#x1f3fd;</span></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form-review "><div class="rplg-row rplg-row-start"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURdBX7EqvZZbz35P6cXEImAsRiiO8jqOcljBiuJJkj-Q3VRNZxyg=s56-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="Stephen K." width="50" height="50" title="Stephen K." onerror="if(this.src!='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png')this.src='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right"><div class="rplg-review-name rplg-trim" title="Stephen K.">Stephen K.</div><div class="rplg-review-time rplg-trim" data-time="1756733675">13:34 01 Sep 25</div><div class="rplg-box-content"><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="5,google,#777"></div><span class="rplg-review-text">I bought a made-to-measure suit from them in May 2025 for a wedding, and I was thrilled with the whole process and final result. Oliver and the team took time to walk me through various colours and fabric options, along with the advantages and disadvantages of each. My three-piece dark green suit is absolutely amazing. Yes, it's more expensive than buying a premium off-the-rack suit, but it fits and feels perfect. I'll be back to Rotknopf for my next suit.</span></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form-review "><div class="rplg-row rplg-row-start"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrPFw2NkeCBOjFrjl5a2VtUqK5CfEFon7cwxe8TfDaCW_Ws4Y=s56-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="Mihály S." width="50" height="50" title="Mihály S." onerror="if(this.src!='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png')this.src='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right"><div class="rplg-review-name rplg-trim" title="Mihály S.">Mihály S.</div><div class="rplg-review-time rplg-trim" data-time="1748341105">10:18 27 May 25</div><div class="rplg-box-content"><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="5,google,#777"></div><span class="rplg-review-text">Extremely helpful staff, high quality work and an overall great experience. Can only recommend!</span></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form-review "><div class="rplg-row rplg-row-start"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7-9NG1oMfRCpcLrTfSUCU0U7qclZ-UyDAZoD5YO1y0Ch5D6U=s56-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="Daniel T." width="50" height="50" title="Daniel T." onerror="if(this.src!='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png')this.src='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right"><div class="rplg-review-name rplg-trim" title="Daniel T.">Daniel T.</div><div class="rplg-review-time rplg-trim" data-time="1731413789">12:16 12 Nov 24</div><div class="rplg-box-content"><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="5,google,#777"></div><span class="rplg-review-text">I did ask them a million years ago to make a hand tailored suit for me. I came there with a quite strange idea but they did handle it without any problem! Since I didn’t change much of my body shape I still can wear it till now. Ok, I did use it only on special occasions. Maybe you remember there guy with the Chefs jacket &#x263a;&#xfe0f;&#x263a;&#xfe0f;&#x263a;&#xfe0f;</span></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form-review "><div class="rplg-row rplg-row-start"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWF063_GxPP86_XomI7fo0-AUzqfY17R6kvoO8zO4Iozi9lPPzM=s56-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="Suhrud A." width="50" height="50" title="Suhrud A." onerror="if(this.src!='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png')this.src='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right"><div class="rplg-review-name rplg-trim" title="Suhrud A.">Suhrud A.</div><div class="rplg-review-time rplg-trim" data-time="1710284035">22:53 12 Mar 24</div><div class="rplg-box-content"><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="5,google,#777"></div><span class="rplg-review-text">My brief was simple: I wanted a classic three-piece suit in blue for my upcoming wedding. I knew roughly what I wanted the finished product to look like, but as they say, the devil is in the details. The team at rotknopf advised me on fabrics, color pairings, lapel style, cut, linings, and all the other small details that turn a good suit into a great one. Over a total of four fittings, the suit was tailored to achieve an optimal fit.Not just that, they also made it so that this became one of the most enjoyable purchase experiences I have ever had. The suit order morphed into an order for a suit + overcoat, and I am all the happier for it.They will definitely see me again!</span></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form-review "><div class="rplg-row rplg-row-start"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUET2TgKhwBXBOdiRIpg34Bq4TWa5lwIDrM_wcp3ZR0zzU-a3TB=s56-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="Nicola P." width="50" height="50" title="Nicola P." onerror="if(this.src!='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png')this.src='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right"><div class="rplg-review-name rplg-trim" title="Nicola P.">Nicola P.</div><div class="rplg-review-time rplg-trim" data-time="1695025262">08:21 18 Sep 23</div><div class="rplg-box-content"><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="5,google,#777"></div><span class="rplg-review-text">Such an amazing tailor. Best experience of my life.The suit turned out fantastic and everyone loved it and complimented it.I'll get all my suits from him from now on.</span></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form-review "><div class="rplg-row rplg-row-start"><div class="rplg-row-left"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png" data-src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzHieKbj7JY32-5oOQKWwOuAi8TuL1GqGKUtinSjbKSGELFfvV=s56-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2" class="rplg-review-avatar rplg-blazy" alt="Qutaiba Z." width="50" height="50" title="Qutaiba Z." onerror="if(this.src!='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png')this.src='https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/google_avatar.png';" ></div><div class="rplg-row-right"><div class="rplg-review-name rplg-trim" title="Qutaiba Z.">Qutaiba Z.</div><div class="rplg-review-time rplg-trim" data-time="1528812375">14:06 12 Jun 18</div><div class="rplg-box-content"><div class="rplg-stars" data-info="5,google,#777"></div><span class="rplg-review-text">Couldn't be any better!My wedding photographers highly recommended this suits shop for me and I will definitely recommend it to my friends and people I know as well.I'm very happy and satisfied with my wedding suit.</span></div></div></div></div><div class="rplg-links"><a href="https://search.google.com/local/reviews?placeid=ChIJ3x35NowHbUcRfjEhQ-ICNhE" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return true;">Alle Rezensionen anzeigen</a></div></div></div><div class="rplg-form-footer"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.rotknopf.at/wp-content/plugins/business-reviews-bundle/assets/img/powered_by_google_on_white.png" alt="powered by Google" width="144" height="18" title="powered by Google"></div></div></div></div><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" alt="js_loader" onload="(function(el, data) { var t = setInterval(function () { if (window.rplg_init_badge_theme){ rplg_init_badge_theme(el, data); clearInterval(t); } }, 200); })(this.parentNode);" data-exec="false" style="display:none"></div>        </div>
						</div>
